getOWSNamespaces

Source: R/OWSNamespace.R
getOWSNamespaces.Rd

getOWSNamespaces gets the list of namespaces registered

Usage

getOWSNamespaces()

Author

Emmanuel Blondel, emmanuel.blondel1@gmail.com
